rows.label: tlk42100121_07_msg0001
rows.name:
Mo-mo...
The breeze feels so nice here, mo...

rows.label: tlk42100121_07_msg0003
rows.name:
T-Takaka is just taking a break,
not slacking off, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100121_07_msg0004
rows.name:
The Sumpkins are having a bumper crop this year,
so much that we can't keep up with the harvest speed, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100121_07_msg0005
rows.name:
At this rate, the Sumpkins we've so carefully raised will
spoil and we won't be able to sell them as products... mo.

rows.label: tlk42100121_07_msg0006
rows.name: If only we had a few more hands... mo.

rows.label: tlk42100121_07_msg0007
rows.name:
Really, mo?!
That would be a huge help, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100121_07_msg0008
rows.name:
Takaka will just slack off a bit more here...
I mean, take a break before heading over, mo!
